OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FOften cloudy this morning with
OL,6,Foccasional outbreaks of mainly light
OL,7,Frain or drizzle. Turning drier and
OL,8,Fbrighter from the north during the
OL,9,Fafternoon, but it will be noticeably
OL,10,Fbreezy, offsetting the warmer
OL,11,Ftemperatures a little.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FWidely dry and bright this
OL,14,Fevening, although still rather breezy.
OL,15,FThen fine and dry overnight with
OL,16,Fmostly clear skies and winds generally
OL,17,Feasing.
OL,18,
OL,19,CSaturday:FDry with variable cloud and
OL,20,Fsome sunny spells Saturday. Breezy
OL,21,Fagain, especially in the north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
