OL,3,GEast
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:
OL,6,FGenerally dry with plenty of fine,
OL,7,Fbright weather expected. Rather cool
OL,8,Fand breezy on Sunday, but turning
OL,9,Fslightly warmer with lighter winds on
OL,10,FMonday and Tuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
